        "pattern": "client_credentials[\"'\\s]*[:=][\"'\\s]*[A-Za-z0-9+/]{40,100}",
        "message": "Twitch OAuth client credentials token detected. Client credentials tokens are used for server-to-server authentication when accessing Twitch API endpoints that don't require user authorization. Exposing client credentials tokens allows unauthorized access to Twitch API functionality, potential rate limit abuse, and access to application-level data. Use secure credential storage and rotate tokens regularly.",
